            <fr:title text="Conditioning Trick FM ">Conditioning Trick <fr:link href="/lipmanFlowMatchingGenerative2023/" title="Flow Matching for Generative Modeling" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/lipmanFlowMatchingGenerative2023/" display-uri="lipmanFlowMatchingGenerative2023" type="local">FM</fr:link> </fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p> Given data distribution <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q(x)]]></fr:tex>, we define an approximation <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p(x)]]></fr:tex> with the form <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[p(x) = \int  p(x \mid  x_1) q(x_1) \mathrm {d}x_{1}]]></fr:tex> In order to ensure <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p(x) \approx  q(x)]]></fr:tex>, we pick <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p(x \mid  x_{1})]]></fr:tex> that concentrates around <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x_{1}]]></fr:tex> i.e. <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p(x \mid  x_{1}) \sim  N(x \mid  x_{1}, \sigma ^2 I)]]></fr:tex> for small <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\sigma ]]></fr:tex>.
 </html:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="/kellenkanarios/" title="Kellen Kanarios" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/kellenkanarios/" display-uri="kellenkanarios" type="local">Kellen Kanarios</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>7</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>9</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:uri>https://kellenkanarios.com/8XAJ/</fr:uri>
                <fr:display-uri>8XAJ</fr:display-uri>
                <fr:route>/8XAJ/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Conditional Vector Field">Conditional Vector Field</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
 We define the <html:em>conditional vector field</html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v_t(\cdot  \mid  x_{1})]]></fr:tex> as the <fr:link href="/008C/" title="Time-dependent vector field" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008C/" display-uri="008C" type="local">vector field</fr:link> that <fr:link href="/008E/" title="Generated probability paths" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008E/" display-uri="008E" type="local">generates</fr:link> the conditional <fr:link href="/008E/" title="Generated probability paths" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008E/" display-uri="008E" type="local">probability path</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p_t(x \mid  x_{1})]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="/kellenkanarios/" title="Kellen Kanarios" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/kellenkanarios/" display-uri="kellenkanarios" type="local">Kellen Kanarios</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>7</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>9</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:uri>https://kellenkanarios.com/373T/</fr:uri>
                <fr:display-uri>373T</fr:display-uri>
                <fr:route>/373T/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Marginal Vector Field">Marginal Vector Field</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
 Given a <fr:link href="/8XAJ/" title="Conditional Vector Field" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/8XAJ/" display-uri="8XAJ" type="local">conditional vector field</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v_t(x \mid  x_{1})]]></fr:tex> we define the <html:em>marginal vector field</html:em> as <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[v_t(x) = \int  v_t(x \mid  x_1) \frac {p(x \mid  x_1) q(x_{1})}{p(t)}]]></fr:tex></html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="/kellenkanarios/" title="Kellen Kanarios" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/kellenkanarios/" display-uri="kellenkanarios" type="local">Kellen Kanarios</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>7</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>9</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:uri>https://kellenkanarios.com/93R8/</fr:uri>
                <fr:display-uri>93R8</fr:display-uri>
                <fr:route>/93R8/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Marginal Generation">Marginal Generation</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Theorem</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Given a <fr:link href="/8XAJ/" title="Conditional Vector Field" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/8XAJ/" display-uri="8XAJ" type="local">conditional vector field</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v_t(x \mid  x_{1})]]></fr:tex> that <fr:link href="/008E/" title="Generated probability paths" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008E/" display-uri="008E" type="local">generates</fr:link> the conditional <fr:link href="/008B/" title="Probablity density path" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008B/" display-uri="008B" type="local">probability path</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p_t(x \mid  x_{1})]]></fr:tex>
 then the <fr:link href="/373T/" title="Marginal Vector Field" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/373T/" display-uri="373T" type="local">marginal vector field</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v_t]]></fr:tex> generates <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p_t]]></fr:tex>, where
 <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[p_t(x) = \int  p_t(x \mid  x_1) q(x_{1})]]></fr:tex></html:p>
 <html:div class="jms-callout" style="
  margin: 1em 0 1em 0.25em;
  padding: 0.5em 1.1em 0.5em 1.2em;
  border-left: 4px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
  "><html:span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);">Proof.</html:span> 
  This follows from just plugging into <fr:link href="/EFN0/" title="Continuity Equation" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/EFN0/" display-uri="EFN0" type="local">continuity equation</fr:link>.
</html:div>
</fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
